        "created_at": "2020-08-06T14:09:53.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Here\u2019s another video from Burgundy, showing d\u2019Auvenay\u2019s Enseign\u00e8res the other day. This parcel was acquired recently, it used to belong to Domaine Jacques Bavard. It\u2019s contiguous with the B\u00e2tard parcel which came from the same source. As you can see, d\u2019Auvenay is treating very regularly, and these vines look very vigorous and healthy. I guess what they say about the water table in Puligny is true\u2026</p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"1torHGESywE\" data-video-title=\"Domaine d'Auvenay's Puligny-Montrachet Les Enseign\u00e8res, August 2020\" data-video-start-time=\"\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1torHGESywE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/1torHGESywE/maxresdefault.jpg\" title=\"Domaine d'Auvenay's Puligny-Montrachet Les Enseign\u00e8res, August 2020\" width=\"\" height=\"\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
