        "created_at": "2020-08-07T15:54:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>William:</p>\n<p>I really dig your \u201cshow, don\u2019t tell\u201d journalism here.</p>\n<p>You may have been on a guided tour, but there\u2019s a hidden camera quality about these posts that I find engrossing. I keep waiting for some functionary to pop out of the bushes and shoo you away!</p>\n<p>I love that common people, not just esteemed critics, can walk the rows of the most exalted vineyards in the world.</p>",
